--------------------------------------------------------
PROJECT GOAL
--------------------------------------------------------

Build an enterprise-grade financial reconciliation engine capable of reconciling multiple financial documents uploaded on two sides.

LEFT SIDE

• Multiple PDFs
• Multiple DOCX
• Multiple Excel Workbooks
• Multiple CSV

RIGHT SIDE

• Multiple PDFs
• Multiple DOCX
• Multiple Excel Workbooks
• Multiple CSV

Users upload files temporarily.

Files are processed entirely in memory.

Nothing is stored permanently unless explicitly exported.

